        "name": "Spell Riposte",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "text": "You attempt to counteract the triggering spell. If the spell would be counteracted, it instead continues with the caster as a target instead of you. *Spell riposte* can't affect spells that aren't targeted (such as area spells).",
